WE KNOW FLOODING
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    The meteorologists said that last month was the wettest March
    in over a decade - but we knew that already. Living between two
    rivers, the Thames and the Crane, we St Margarethians have seen the
    evidence with our own eyes. Twickenham and Richmond riversides were
    flooded and so were Radnor Gardens, Ranelagh Drive and towpaths
    from Teddington to Kew and beyond. Cars bobbed about axle deep
    in murky waters...

